(23, 'Contesto', 'contesto', 'IntegrART - Contesto', 'IntegrART - Contesto', 'website', '/assets/cache/1200/630/media/Galerie Aktuell/Une bouche Lila Derridj by Mark Maborough.jpg', 'Con il progetto di rete IntegrART, il Percento culturale Migros si impegna nel sostenere l’inclusione artistica e sociale delle persone disabili. Dal 2007 il progetto biennale, divenuto punto di incontro per i festival di tutto il Paese, organizza simposi e presenta produzioni teatrali nazionali e internazionali, in collaborazione con partner.', 'IntegrART - Contesto', '', 'IntegrART, Percento culturale Migros, inclusione, artisti disabili, simposio, produzioni teatrali inclusive, progetto di rete, diversity, diversità, empowerment, movimento per la disabilità, accessibilità, festival inclusivo, arte inclusiva, cultura inclusiva, società inclusiva, Isabella Spirig, Nina Mühlemann, Tanja Erhart, Emanuel Rosenberg', 'Con il progetto di rete IntegrART, il Percento culturale Migros si impegna nel sostenere l’inclusione artistica e sociale delle persone disabili. Dal 2007 il progetto biennale, divenuto punto di incontro per i festival di tutto il Paese, organizza simposi e presenta produzioni teatrali nazionali e internazionali, in collaborazione con partner.', 'Percento culturale Migros', 'index, follow', 4, 3, 1, '2019-03-04 10:45:40'),
(24, 'Symposium', 'symposium', 'IntegrART - Symposium', 'IntegrART - Symposium', 'website', '/assets/cache/1200/630/media/FB/HappyIsland-LaRibot-DancandocomaDiferenca-byJulioSilvaCastro.jpg', 'The perspectives of disabled people change the art world. On 2 May and 3 May 2019, the seventh IntegrART Symposium takes place at Gessnerallee Zurich and Tanzhaus Zurich. Entitled ‘It’s a Matter of Perspective’, the symposium will explore the ways in which non-normative perspectives expand different art forms and cross (aesthetic) boundaries.', 'IntegrART - Symposium', '', 'Access Aesthetics, perspective. IntegrART, Migros Culture Percentage, inclusion, artists with a disability, handicaped artist, handicaped person, symposium, networking project, diversity, empowerment, disability rights movement, accessibility, inclusive festival, inclusive dance company, inclusive arts, inclusive culture, inclusive society, Isabella Spirig, Nina Mühlemann, Tanja Erhart', 'The perspectives of disabled people change the art world. On 2 May and 3 May 2019, the seventh IntegrART Symposium takes place at Gessnerallee Zurich and Tanzhaus Zurich. Entitled ‘It’s a Matter of Perspective’, the symposium will explore the ways in which non-normative perspectives expand different art forms and cross (aesthetic) boundaries.', 'Migros Culture Percentage', 'index, follow', 2, 4, 1, '2019-03-07 20:53:14'),
(25, 'Colloque', 'colloque', 'IntegrART - Colloque', 'IntegrART - Colloque', 'website', '', '', 'IntegrART - Colloque', '', 'IntegrART, Pour-cent culturel Migros, inclusion, artistes en situation de handicap, artiste handicapé, personnes handicapées, colloque, production inclusive, projet de mise en réseau, diversity, diversité, empowerment, accessibilité, accès aux personnes handicapées, festival inclusif, compagnie de danse integrative, arts inclusifs, culture inclusive, société inclusive, Isabella Spirig, Nina Mühlemann, Tanja Erhart', 'La septième édition du colloque IntegrART se déroulera les 2 et 3 mai 2019 dans les locaux de la Gessnerallee Zürich et du Tanzhaus Zürich. Intitulée «It’s a Matter of Perspective», la manifestation examinera dans quelle mesure les perspectives hors norme enrichissent les différentes formes artistiques et font voler en éclat les barrières (esthétiques). ', 'Pour-cent culturel Migros', 'index, follow', 3, 4, 1, '2019-02-22 21:06:39'),
(26, 'Simposio', 'simposio', 'IntegrART - Simposio', 'IntegrART - Simposio', 'website', '', '', 'IntegrART - Simposio', '', 'IntegrART, Percento culturale Migros, inclusione, artisti disabili, simposio, produzioni teatrali inclusive, progetto di rete, diversity, diversità, empowerment, movimento per la disabilità, accessibilità, festival inclusivo, arte inclusiva, cultura inclusiva, società inclusiva, Isabella Spirig, Nina Mühlemann, Tanja Erhart, Emanuel Rosenberg', 'Il 2 e 3 maggio 2019 a Zurigo, presso il teatro Gessnerallee e la Tanzhaus, si tiene il settimo simposio IntegrART. Durante il convegno, dal titolo «It’s a Matter of Perspective», la discussione verte sulle diverse prospettive che, situate oltre i canoni tradizionali, arricchiscono le forme artistiche scardinandone i confini (estetici).', 'Percento culturale Migros', 'index, follow', 4, 4, 1, '2019-02-22 21:24:19'),
(27, 'Performances', 'performances', 'IntegrART - Performances', 'IntegrART - Performances', 'website', '/assets/cache/1200/630/media/FB/HappyIsland-LaRibot-DancandocomaDiferenca-byJulioSilvaCastro.jpg', 'From 21 May until 9 June 2019 the partner festivals of IntegrART show selected stage productions by and with disabled artists. Two solo artists, from France and Mozambique, as well as a dance company from Portugal are coming to the Wildwuchs Festival in Basel, BewegGrund in Berne, Out of the Box in Geneva and to the ORME in Lugano. Additionally, IntegrART and its partner festivals are presenting a short piece which is the result of a new, inclusive training module taught for the first time as part of the bachelor’s course in Contemporary Dance at the Zurich University of the Arts.', 'IntegrART - Performances', '', 'IntegrART, Migros Culture Percentage, inclusion, artists with a disability, handicaped artist, handicaped person, inclusive production, networking project, diversity, empowerment, disability rights movement, accessibility, inclusive festival, inclusive dance company, inclusive arts, inclusive culture, inclusive society, Maria Tembe, Lila Derridj, La Ribot, Cie Dançando com a Diferença, ZHdK Stage Lab, Une bouche, Solo for Maria, Happy Island, Orme Festival, Wildwuchs Festival, Beweggrund.Das Festival, Out of the Box ', 'From 21 May until 9 June 2019 the partner festivals of IntegrART show selected stage productions by and with disabled artists. Two solo artists, from France and Mozambique, as well as a dance company from Portugal are coming to the Wildwuchs Festival in Basel, BewegGrund in Berne, Out of the Box in Geneva and to the ORME in Lugano. Additionally, IntegrART and its partner festivals are presenting a short piece which is the result of a new, inclusive training module taught for the first time as part of the bachelor’s course in Contemporary Dance at the Zurich University of the Arts.', 'Migros Culture Percentage', '', 2, 5, 1, '2019-03-07 20:56:43'),
(28, 'Représentations', 'representations', 'IntegrART - Représentations', 'IntegrART - Représentations', 'website', '', '', 'IntegrART - Représentations', '', 'IntegrART, Pour-cent culturel Migros, inclusion, artistes en situation de handicap, artiste handicapé, personnes handicapées, production inclusive, projet de mise en réseau, diversity, diversité, empowerment, accessibilité, accès aux personnes handicapées, festival inclusif, compagnie de danse integrative, arts inclusifs, culture inclusive, société inclusive, Maria Tembe, Lila Derridj, La Ribot, Cie Dançando com a Diferença, ZHdK Stage Lab, Happy Island, Une bouche, Solo for Maria, Orme Festival, Wildwuchs Festival, Beweggrund.Das Festival, Beweggrund, Out of the Box', 'Du 21 mai au 9 juin 2019, les festivals partenaires d’IntegrART présenteront sur leurs scènes des productions créées et interprétées par des artistes en situation de handicap. Deux solistes de France et du Mozambique ainsi qu’une compagnie de danse portugaise seront à l’affiche du Wildwuchs Festival à Bâle, de BewegGrund à Berne, d’Out of the Box à Genève et de l’ORME à Lugano. IntegrART et ses festivals partenaires présenteront en outre dans une pièce courte les résultats du module de formation inclusive intégré, pour la première fois au printemps 2019, au cycle de bachelor en danse contemporaine de la Haute école d’art de Zurich.', 'Pour-cent culturel Migros', 'index, follow', 3, 5, 1, '2019-02-22 21:05:24'),
(29, 'Spettacoli', 'spettacoli', 'IntegrART - Spettacoli', 'IntegrART - Spettacoli', 'website', '', '', 'IntegrART - Spettacoli', '', 'IntegrART, Percento culturale Migros, inclusione, artisti disabili, simposio, produzioni teatrali inclusive, progetto di rete, diversity, diversità, empowerment, movimento per la disabilità, accessibilità, festival inclusivo, arte inclusiva, cultura inclusiva, società inclusiva, Emanuel Rosenberg, Maria Tembe, La Ribot, Lila Derridj, Cie Dançando com a Diferença, Une bouche, Solo for Maria, Happy Island, ZHdK Stage Lab, Orme Festival, Wildwuchs Festival, Beweggrund, Beweggrund.Das Festival, Out of the Box', 'Dal 21 maggio al 9 giugno 2019, i festival associati a IntegrART mettono in scena quattro produzioni teatrali scelte, opera di artisti disabili e da loro interpretate. Due artiste soliste dalla Francia e dal Mozambico e una compagnia di danza portoghese saranno ospiti al Wildwuchs Festival di Basilea, al BewegGrund di Berna, all’Out of the Box di Ginevra e all’ORME di Lugano. Inoltre, con un breve spettacolo, IntegrART e i festival associati presentano i risultati ottenuti nell’ambito di un modulo formativo inclusivo proposto per la prima volta nella primavera del 2019 nel ciclo di studio bachelor in danza contemporanea, presso la scuola superiore delle arti di Zurigo ZHdK. ', 'Percento culturale Migros', 'index, follow', 4, 5, 1, '2019-02-22 21:23:07'),
